    </div>
    <div class="banner7">
      <div class="main1">
        <div class="order">
          <div class="o-title">活动期间内，累计投资排行在前5名获得元旦红包：</div>
              <div class="o-con">
              <p>第一名：<span>2888</span>元</p>
                <p>第二名：<span>1888</span>元</p>
                <p>第三名：<span>888</span>元</p>
                <p>第四名：<span>588</span>元</p>
                <p>第五名：<span>188</span>元</p>
              </div>
        </div>
          <div class="lucky-box">
